thread.title: BRIEF-Teleste Oyj Q4 Operating Profit Falls To EUR 0.3 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Teleste Oyj Q4 Operating Profit Falls To EUR 0.3 Million
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - Teleste Oyj:
* Q4 NET SALES EUR 58.7 MILLION VERSUS EUR 68.6 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 OPERATING PROFIT EUR 0.3 MILLION VERSUS EUR 4.3 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 ORDERS RECEIVED EUR 66.7 MILLION VERSUS EUR 64.6 MILLION YEAR AGO
* EXPECTS COMPANY‘S NET SALES TO INCREASE IN 2018 COMPARED WITH 2017 (EUR 234.6 MILLION)
* 2018 OPERATING RESULT IS EXPECTED TO BE CLEARLY POSITIVE * ‍DIRECTORS PROPOSES A DIVIDEND OF EUR 0.10 (0.25) PER OUTSTANDING SHARE.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
